# Licensed/proprietary typefaces must never be committed. Every face we ship is
# self-hosted and openly licensed (Archivo + JetBrains Mono, both .woff2), so a
# .otf/.ttf appearing here is almost always a brand font that cannot be
# redistributed. Add an explicit exception if that ever stops being true.
*.otf
*.ttf
